BUGS
----

This is beta software!
This is still considered a beta/testing stages

Please report bugs to mplayerd-bugs@signuts.net

When reporting a bug please include the version of mplayer and mplayerd.
Elaborate as much as possible, as if you were explaining the problem
to a two year old =)


KNOWN BUGS
----------
- using -loop 0 is a bad idea, if something goes wrong it's very difficult for mplayerd to recover
  and maintain the proper state
- sending 'pause' command many times is rapid succession will crash mplayerd

